-- Essar Oil Sells $147 Million of Bonds to Founder to Fund Expansion Plans
-- Tuhin Kar
-- 2010-07-09T12:10:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-09/essar-oil-sells-147-million-of-bonds-to-founder-to-fund-expansion-plans.html

          
          
             Essar Oil Ltd. issued $147 million of
bonds due September 2028 to founder company Essar Energy
Holdings Ltd. to part finance expansion programs, according to a
statement today on the Bombay Stock Exchange.  
          
          


  


        